{"tid":2281414,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Switch種植稻米日式遊戲 ｜《天穗之咲稻姬》","createTime":"2020-11-11T07:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T04:41:10.000Z","uid":129010,"like":7,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c3ee823a7a1d2c943039e85f43bcfe13c575787d","tid":2281414,"uid":129010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:26:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tiwoaDBzdr0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtiwoaDBzdr0&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEfGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=792a95e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tiwoaDBzdr0</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zwqVTDu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzwqVTDu.png&h=2f299ef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好，我係鯧鯧鯧。今次來試玩新的遊戲《天穗之咲稻姬》。呢個遊戲係一個日本二人團隊開發出來。遊戲重點去一個被鬼族支配的「日之惠島」上邊，透過種植稻米令（犯咗錯嘅）女主角變得強大的和風動作。"},{"pid":"cb0b35fa430c523a367feb1734f0f13ef28d437d","tid":2281414,"uid":225210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:36:53.000Z","msg":"有啲興趣玩"},{"pid":"381587a53d01ce592cc0be4b2f67db8d95e082c5","tid":2281414,"uid":1915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:37:41.000Z","msg":"乜鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ca47015cfd5acb8b583d4564b98b13c931d093","tid":2281414,"uid":337058,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:59:39.000Z","msg":"呢隻有興趣，但只賣$300 有點擔心內容少"},{"pid":"366fad9d6ea97e77da7174797037acc22ba8d63a","tid":2281414,"uid":178533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T19:57:32.000Z","msg":"玩到第3年，暫時覺得唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c15f077505b13795cf0d5eb13121972bad98281","tid":2281414,"uid":121076,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T20:03: